item.title: Ultimate frisbee: Disc doctors’ october digest
item.author: Imperial discDoctors,
item.description: Imperial College’s Ultimate Team, disc Doctors, had a busy October full of tournaments and socials. Just in the first month of term we sent beginner teams to 3 different tournaments across England in: London, Brighton, and Norwich. In addition, one of the tournaments, “Skyde Park” was hosted by …
